com.idibon.api.model

Class IdibonHash

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.idibon.api.model.IdibonHash
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Collection, Document, Task

    public abstract class IdibonHash
extends Object
    Base class for all data model objects that are loadable via direct HTTP GET operations from the Idibon API.
